title: Testing The Latest Release of DTOS Gnu/Linux
description:
DTOS is an Arch-based GNU/Linux distribution that is built around the Qtile window manager, Emacs and dmscripts.  In this video, I'm running through a quick installation and first look of the latest build of DTOS.

REFERENCED:
